——干垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">公仔——可回收垃圾</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">美甲类废旧垃圾分类</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">光疗甲、假指甲/手指甲、脚指甲——干垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">指甲刀/指甲剪——可回收垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">锡纸/指甲锉——干垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">胶水/万能胶水/假睫毛胶水/废胶水——干垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">湿巾/纸巾——干垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">美甲灯——可回收垃圾</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">摄影类废旧垃圾分类</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">照相机/旧相机/幕布——可回收垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">包装纸盒/壁纸——干垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">灯/白炽灯/玻璃灯罩/钨丝灯/钨丝灯泡——可回收垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">LED灯/LED灯泡/废弃灯泡/废旧灯泡/废 荧光灯管——有害垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">笔记本电池/充电电池/电池板/废电池——有害垃圾</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">废交卷/交卷底片——有害垃圾</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">除了这些专业废旧垃圾，还有哪些常接触的呢？</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">零食袋/垃圾袋/塑料袋/包装袋——干垃圾</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">猫零食——湿垃圾</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">餐饮外卖盒/外卖餐具/外卖塑料盒——干垃圾</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">标有回收标志外卖盒/外卖订单纸——可回收垃圾</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">剩菜剩饭——湿垃圾</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">也就是说，各位小伙伴们，吃完的外卖，剩菜剩饭是湿垃圾，装剩菜剩饭的盒子又是干垃圾，如果你一起扔，那就×××，罚款就可以了解一下了。你是不是准备放弃吃饭了呢？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">保护环境人人有责，看了很多环保的片子，垃圾分类是开始很麻烦却对未来和环境有益的事情。大家一起加油吧。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 30px\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><br/></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>','',NULL,NULL,'','','39.149.1.107'),(162,31,'<p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">两会召开，总理的政府工作报告正式发布，在报告中，有几个巨额数字，与我们密切相关。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">1000亿元</span></strong><strong style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">用于职工技能提升和转岗转业培训</span></strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">作为我国经济发展的风向标，在本次报告中，总理在很重要的位置提及关于“青年技能立业”，提出“加快培养国家发展急需的各类技术技能人才，让更多青年凭借一技之长实现人生价值，让三百六十行人才荟萃，繁星璀璨。”。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">以及政府将投入1000亿元，用于职工技能提升和转岗转业培训。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">院校是技能立业的起点</span></strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">技能院校在教育中的角色占比越来越大，技能类院校与其他院校最不同的一点就是，让技术和实践说话，不在纸上谈兵，学会的意义不是背会，是可以动手实践。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">消费升级&nbsp;美业不再是小生意</span></strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">服务领域和其他高科技领域一样，同属于专长技能人才，也是人才缺口的大项。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">美容美发、化妆摄影这些兴趣消费已逐渐成为主流，甚至是经济市场的大蛋糕。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">时尚产业已经成为消费升级中，最受带动的行业之一。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">千亿市场的大蛋糕，别只能闻味儿</span></strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">美容院，摄影工作室，美发店，化妆师的日常，美甲店这些人均消费是多少，你不问别人，你自己也一定感受过，你就付出过多少钱？</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">上个十年，是科技领域爆发的十年，而这个十年，服务领域的势头已经起来了，如果还在徘徊，还在犹豫，下一个十年，你还是只能在寻找机会，而不能享受这份成果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">美容、美发、摄影、化妆、美甲、纹绣</span></strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px;\">新学期课程已全面开启，80%的实操学习和更多的真人实践机会，在等着你。国家和学校都已经给你铺路了，你还在观望么？</span></p><p><br style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p><p><br/></p>','',NULL,NULL,'','','39.149.1.107');
INSERT INTO `rc_addonarticle` VALUES (163,31,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">按我国现在的发展速度，在不久的将来，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">很多流水线工作会被机器人取代，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">就业形势越来越严峻，特别是下岗职工、</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">农名工，初高中毕业生，退役军人，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">他们该何去何从？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">/工厂机器人在流水线上工作/</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2019全国两会，《政府工作报告》指出，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今年要对高职院校实施扩招，人数是100万人，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">让更多青年凭借一技之长实现人生价值！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">鼓励更多高中毕业生、下岗职工、农名工，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">退役军人等报考职业院校。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这也关乎着大范围的家庭如何做出教育选择，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关系着我国职业教育的改革发展方向！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">什么是职业学校？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(45, 44, 64); letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">职业学校教学偏重于技能的教学。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高职教育由省政府管理，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">省政府会在国家政策的指导下，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以适应社会的就业需要为目标，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">主要培养学生的技术应用能力等，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">强调理论与实际应用的结合，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">毕业生具有直接上岗工作的能力。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">职业院校要扩招100万学生，那考生和家长会买账吗？？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我国作为第二大经济体，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由高速发展逐渐走上了高质发展的道路，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我国急需大量的高职人才，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拥有一技之长的高职人才就业前景相当不错，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为何某些考生和家长会有顾虑？</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">造成这样的原因无非有两种：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.用人单位学历“高消费”的人资市场环境，非985、211、本科生不录！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.学生和家长的惯性思维。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我国学历高消费的现象一直很严重，很多企业岗位录用人才不以岗位需求为目的，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而是看学历的高低，进而使中国家长和学生不得不追求更高的学历，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以获得就业主动权。这样导致的后果是，很多基础岗位也有高学历者参与竞争，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">导致就业生态环境不平衡！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我国过去大学学历者少，所以高学历具有较高的社会价值，几十年下来，形成了家长和学生的固有思维！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着社会的发展，大学学历普遍泛滥，且很多专业偏理论知识居多，没有之前那么大的社会价值。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">毕业后，许多大学生的收入非常低，远不如许多没读过大学的人的收入高，这样的事情大家可以看看自己的身边，都普遍存在。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">学了一技之长的人，根本不用担心丢掉饭碗，反而很多大学生就业压力会更大，我们不得不承认，只有20%的高学历者才有更多好的工作机会，排在后面的人同职业院校的学生相差无几。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对高学历的过度消费，导致诞生了很多五花八门的大学，很多学子根本无法从这些“大学”中学到真才实学，白白浪费了四年的光阴和大好的青春，拿到的文凭社会根本不认！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不是任何岗位都追求尽量高的学历，人才有很多种才能类型。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">每年毕业季，都有这样的现象存在，就是大学毕业的学生就业难，而招聘单位招人难。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">学校学习的知识和社会上的许多工作岗位并不相关。不少工作不需要大学学历！往往导致的结果是，很多大学生去做了一些低工资且不需要大学学历的工作，导致了我国人才的大量浪费！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">社会金字塔需要基座</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不需要也不能人人都去做塔尖。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">政府在两会上采取了果断措施，以压倒性扭转畸形就业生态之势！指出2019年高职&nbsp;扩招100万人。让更多人能够真正学到一技之长，保障就业！从而实现自己的人生价值！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(122, 121, 146); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-